Sentencas: An adaptation of the Schwickerath crack initiation test (ISO 9693) was used to determine the bonding strength between an anode support and three different cathodes with a solid oxide fuel cell interconnect.
Titulo: Determination of the bonding strength in solid oxide fuel cells' interfaces by Schwickerath crack initiation test

Sentencas: Interfacial elemental characterization of the interfaces was carried out by SEM/EDS analysis on fracture surfaces to investigate the bonding mechanisms.
Titulo: Determination of the bonding strength in solid oxide fuel cells' interfaces by Schwickerath crack initiation test

Sentencas: SEM/EDS of fresh fractures were also performed to determine the cohesion/adhesion mechanism of bonding.
Titulo: Determination of the bonding strength in solid oxide fuel cells' interfaces by Schwickerath crack initiation test

Sentencas: Calculations of the residual stresses were determined by finite element simulation using ANSYS, based on thermo-mechanical properties of the materials obtained by measurement, calculation or literature.
Titulo: Determination of the bonding strength in solid oxide fuel cells' interfaces by Schwickerath crack initiation test
